    <scopecontent id="scopecontent-1.8.3">
      <head>Scope and Content</head>
      <p>Two volumes containing letters, postcards, clippings, and typed poems from Upton Sinclair and Mary Craig Sinclair to Ryo Namikawa. Also includes 8 volumes of Upton Sinclair's works translated into Japanese by Namikawa with a holograph note in Namikawa's hand.</p>
    </scopecontent>
